程序包 com.misfit.misfitsdk.device

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    MFDevice
    MFDevice provides operations of a device support.
    MFFlashDevice
    MFDevice for Flash as MFDevice instance is created before model name is known in connect task, MFFlashDevice supports Device type update to FlashLink after connect
    MFIwcDevice
    MFDevice for IWC(Silveratta)
    MFMKIIDevice
    MFDevice subclass for Shine MK II
    MFRayDevice
    MFDevice subclass for Ray(RAY)
    MFShine2Device
    MFDevice subclass for Shine2(Pluto)
    MFShineDevice
    MFDevice child class for Shine device
    MFSpeedoDevice
    MFDevice subclass for Speedo Shine NOTE: currently, its operation is totally the same with MFShineDevice
    MFSwarovskiDevice
    subclass of MFDevice for Swarovski Shine
